{"tid":1933020,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土] 2D Pixel 香港獨立遊戲: Nameless Cat","createTime":"2020-03-19T05:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T05:19:13.000Z","uid":238862,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3a0d8bdfe3ab398ba794528782c3d9d946d6ad","tid":1933020,"uid":238862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>[本土] 2D Pixel 獨立遊戲: Nameless Cat</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PoEqg_g83hg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPoEqg_g83hg&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=00f887f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PoEqg_g83hg</a><br />\n<br />\n香港本土 2D Pixel Platformer<br />\n曾經係台灣攞過巴哈姆特既ACG佳作獎，宜家做緊公開測試<br />\nBeta Link: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.kotobagames.namelesscat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fapps%2Ftesting%2Fcom.kotobagames.namelesscat&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=550ea27a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.kotobagames.namelesscat</a><br />\n<br />\nAndriod 預先注冊可以點另外呢條Link，暫時隻Game未有 iOS版本<br />\n預先注冊: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kotobagames.namelesscat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.kotobagames.namelesscat&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=780856d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kotobagames.namelesscat</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲主要講述一隻貓貓集齊45粒龍珠翻屋企既故事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TygcqFo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTygcqFo.jpg&h=7e4cd5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中後期操作都幾難，有心理準備要死好多次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbYqLFs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbYqLFs.jpg&h=3bcf3d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但連續死亡唔會跳廣告，所以唔洗擔心睇廣告睇到嬲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ6f7TS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ6f7TS.jpg&h=06ebc246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以多啲支持吓本土嘅遊戲製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}